816, 129.5901, 131.3734, 132.927, 136.1519, 136.4744, 134.8071, 135.2927, 135.3194, 134.4719, 133.4649, 132.9016, 132.4066, 131.9433, 131.6806, 131.0548, 130.6439, 130.4268, 130.2958, 129.756, 129.3508, 129.3632, 129.5166, 129.723, 129.4517, 129.1629, 129.4484, 130.3628, 130.2688, 129.6332, 130.0415, 130.3425, 130.7785, 131.9594, 131.7694, 130.5927, 131.1178, 131.2882, 131.3275, 133.0585, 135.4674, 135.3606, 135.3212, 135.7277, 136.076, 136.7203, 137.9322, 136.9361, 136.3314, 135.9741, 134.4895, 134.462, 133.9536, 133.2274, 133.1478, 133.4679, 134.1681, 133.7916, 133.899, 133.0414, 132.8985, 133.3413, 132.8419, 133.733, 133.7206, 133.4109, 134.5078, 134.0556, 134.9344, 135.7056, 136.5237, 137.3697, 137.1428, 137.6276, 137.1735, 136.3448, 135.6745, 135.7749, 135.0139, 135.9702, 136.2623, 137.5571, 138.4056, 139.4281, 141.0588, 142.3232, 143.1114, 141.3353, 141.2463, 141.2392, 140.787, 142.3843, 141.6831, 141.3488, 140.2871, 140.6693, 140.0733, 140.923, 139.9908, 140.2648, 142.291, 141.4306, 140.0692, 139.3079, 138.5425, 137.9695, 138.7525, 138.2994, 138.814, 138.2835, 138.3599, 138.7332, 138.9747, 139.6427, 139.554, 138.7066, 139.1188, 140.0046, 141.194, 139.1896, 137.6844, 138.9541, 139.1637, 139.8482, 140.2756, 139.515, 139.844, 140.1929, 140.4081, 141.015, 141.9197, 142.2921, 143.0186, 143.6698, 144.7227, 146.4897, 146.6858, 145.596, 146.7646, 148.7592, 148.2052, 150.1046, 151.8423, 150.3094, 152.4983, 153.106, 157.013, 157.8552, 157.8212, 156.4606, 156.8512], "summary_html": "<h1>基于商品期货期限结构的投资策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略利用商品期货的期限结构（展期收益率 Roll Yield）来推断商品的短期供需状况，进而预测价格走势。当市场处于远月贴水（backwardation）状态时，通常意味着库存偏低、近月价格受到支撑，适合做多；反之近月贴水（contango）时库存偏高，适合做空。策略通过三层过滤提升信号质量：(1) 累积展期收益的动量变化捕捉期限结构的趋势性变化；(2) 滚动窗口筛选 TS 策略历史盈利的品种（排除期限结构逻辑不适用的品种）；(3) 价格动量确认信号方向一致性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.78</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.2%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>9.3%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-15.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.84</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.94</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.64 / 1.02</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.44</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.17</span></td><td>1.01</td><td>1.4</td><td>1.63</td><td>0.9</td><td>0.76</td><td>0.49</td><td>0.56</td><td>1.5</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.04</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>rycumprod</code></td><td>展期收益累乘</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>61</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>29.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>16.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>核心因子 -- 展期收益率（使用真实 <code>ry</code> 字段）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">RY = \\frac{P_N - P_F}{P_F} \\times \\frac{365}{DTM_F - DTM_N}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">P_N</span> 为近月合约价格，<span class=\"math-tex\">P_F</span> 为远月合约价格，<span class=\"math-tex\">DTM</span> 为距到期日天数。</p>\n<p>最优变体使用累积展期收益 <code>rycumprod</code> 的 60 日动量作为信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ryc\\_mom} = \\frac{\\text{rycumprod}_t}{\\text{rycumprod}_{t-60}} - 1</div>\n<p>截面排名 → 连续信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal} = (\\text{rank}_{cs}(\\text{ryc\\_mom}) - 0.5) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<p>TS_Roll 品种筛选：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{roll\\_pass}_i = \\mathbb{1}\\left[\\sum_{k=t-M}^{t} \\text{sign}(ry_k^i) \\cdot r_{k+1}^i &gt; 0\\right], \\quad M = 180</div>\n<p>动量确认（短期 20 日 + 长期 60 日同向）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{mom\\_dir} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if } r_{20} &gt; 0 \\text{ and } r_{60} &gt; 0 \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if } r_{20} &lt; 0 \\text{ and } r_{60} &lt; 0 \\\\ 0 &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>最终信号 = signal <span class=\"math-tex\">\\times</span> roll_pass <span class=\"math-tex\">\\times</span> mom_confirm，再经 vol-parity 缩放。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>实现4个因子变体（TS/TS_Roll/TS_MOM/TS_Roll_MOM），使用ry_ema信号</td><td>CS+TS组合信号(0.6/0.4)，MOM(20/60)确认，M=180 roll filter，vol-parity sizing</td><td><strong>Sharpe 0.91</strong> (TSRM_h10_raw)，所有gate通过</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>尝试推高：strict IC gate、h=8、M=120/240网格、strict MOM(0.1x)</td><td>更多参数组合探索，CS/TS归一化自动启用</td><td>Sharpe 持平 0.91，CS/TS归一化反而降低效果</td></tr><tr><td>R3 (关键转折)</td><td>R2停滞，分析根因：2023年Sharpe为负拖累，TS组分噪声大</td><td><strong>引入rycumprod动量因子</strong>代替ry_ema作为截面信号；尝试不同CS/TS权重；更长MOM(40/120)</td><td><strong>Sharpe 跃升至 1.06</strong>，2023年Sharpe从-0.15转正至0.22</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>：R3引入<code>rycumprod</code>的60日动量作为因子。rycumprod是展期收益的累积乘积，其动量变化比原始ry更平滑、信噪比更高。这个改进使2023年从亏损转为盈利，整体Sharpe从0.91提升至1.06。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：全商品期货（72个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>使用字段</strong>：<code>ry</code>（展期收益率）、<code>rycumprod</code>（累积展期收益）、<code>close</code>（收盘价）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>：10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>多空比例</strong>：多14.3%、空12.7%、空仓73%</li>\n<li><strong>盈利集中品种</strong>：HC（热卷）、JM（焦煤）、I（铁矿石）、P（棕榈油）、RB（螺纹钢）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：与因子库中dongfang多因子相关性0.50（边界），但因子逻辑和数据来源完全不同（carry因子 vs 多因子组合）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>M</code></td><td><code>180</code></td><td>TS_Roll window</td></tr><tr><td><code>RYC_MOM_PERIOD</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>rycumprod momentum lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>MOM_SHORT</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>momentum short period (tag A)</td></tr><tr><td><code>MOM_LONG</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>momentum long period (tag A)</td></tr><tr><td><code>NEUTRAL_MULT</code></td><td><code>0.3</code></td><td>momentum neutral multiplier</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.8s</li>\n</ul>"}